{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC04_JUR_040.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x125,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Wh-Wh-Wh-What's...that noise!<CR>...Thunder?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x129,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No... Get down and stay quiet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That's...a dragon! Amazing...<CR>This is my first time seeing one!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Plus, it was an adult. Looks like it was out hunting nearby."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Huh? How could you tell it was hunting?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "His claws were tainted with blood.<CR>Plus, his stomach was slightly swollen."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Wooow, I didn't even notice. Juris, you have really good eyes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Being sharp-sighted is a huntsman's ultimate weapon. I can distinguish a person's face from the next mountain."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "We would've been in danger if he was hungry. Looks like we narrowly escaped from death."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "We should leave this area just in case. There's a strong possibility that he'll be back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "That dragon sure looks big and strong... It nearly scared me half to death."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It was just like the dragons I saw in storybooks when I was younger. Do you know \"The Dragon and the Girl\"?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "It's a about a girl who rides on the back of an old dragon, and they go traveling around the world..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I used to admire that girl. I hoped I could be just like her and ride on a dragon's back one day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That was my dream, but now that I've seen a real one, I'm not so sure about that anymore..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, you should probably give up on that dream."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Dragons, as individuals, are tyrants... They proudly display their prominent strength to the world."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "For dragons, all living creatures, besides other dragons, are all considered to be food."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "With one slash, their claws can tear up an entire herd of cattle, and the fire they breathe can burn down a village."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "But you'll only be hunted if you carelessly approach them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Thankfully, though, it's been a long time since they've caused any real damage to people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I-I see. I guess I really shouldn't think about riding on their back..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "My goal is to eventually defeat him.<CR>As one who was born into my family,<CR>he's the one I must challenge."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? That's impossible, even for you! He's too big!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "It's not impossible. As a matter of fact, my family has fought many dragons."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "A few of them even succeeded in hunting them. Slaying dragons is closely tied to my family's fate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "So you come from a long line of dragon hunters...? Juris, your family is beyond amazing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "But, it's still dangerous,<CR>so you shouldn't do it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm aware of my situation.<CR>I don't plan on losing my life,<CR>leaving my sister all alone."
        }
    ]
}